       The Energonian shuttles quickly picked up Scayther, Aleo, Celeno, 
Octipite, Alecto, Kali, and Darkfate. They would stand little chance of a 
hard battle arising in this situation. Ominous commanded they stay and fight.
       "Blast them agian, and Quasar, repair the left Naucel. Its leaking 
energon from Aleo's blast." Ominous said. To the left of the main shuttle, 
Akrons shuttle made a sharp about face and sent three energon missles raining 
down on Aleo's vessle.
       As for Greven, Ominous targeted him agian and fired. This time only 
two blasts from the Tripulse canon. He needed to save as much energy as 
possible.
       Venus, in the smaller shuttle to the right, begins to ready weapons 
for the upcoming vessles.


       Hell Beast looked to Shockwave. "Were packed and ready. Detenators are 
placed throughout the cave. We can leave now. Take us to the new base." He 
glanced at the transport shuttles and the team of Predacons piloting them. 
The Neo Deception Empire was just beginning.
